量分别为55.0万和41.7万，虽仍居前列，但环比降幅均超过七成，表明本轮下行并非局部波动，而是区域性的业务收缩。这一拐点式变化发生在4月，需警惕季节性因素之外的供应链调整或外贸需求走弱影响。\\n\\n从结构上看，大连港在TEU吞吐量上继续保持区域领先，约为营口港的1.3倍，区域集聚效应明显。其余城市如丹东、盘锦及绥中贡献极低，合计不足总量的10%，显示集装箱运输资源高度集中于核心港口。当前格局下，大连与营口两港合计占比超九成，区域物流网络依赖度高，抗风险能力面临考验。\\n\\n货物吨数（tonQ）同步环比下降44.2%，但降幅小于TEU量，暗示单箱载重或货值结构可能发生变化，或轻质货物出港比例减少。结合TEU量断崖式下跌，需关注出口订单可持续性及腹地企业出货节\"}, \"status\": \"ok\", \"span_id\": \"1263a9ed\", \"task_id\": \"T002\", \"span_type\": \"llm_call\"}','2026-04-24 09:41:31'),(1421,'653225de-8256-4d93-8f78-c32cdad2f9f8','tool','execution',33781,'{\"error\": null, \"event\": \"tool_call_end\", \"status\": \"success\", \"call_id\": \"T002#1\", \"preview\": {\"keys\": [\"summary_stats\", \"growth_rates\", \"narrative\"], \"output_type\": \"json\"}, \"task_id\": \"T002\", \"skill_id\": \"skill_desc_analysis\", \"error_category\": null}','2026-04-24 09:41:31'),(1422,'653225de-8256-4d93-8f78-c32cdad2f9f8','phase','execution',33811,'{\"done\": 2, \"node\": \"execution\", \"event\": \"phase_exit\", \"failed\": 0, \"running\": 0, \"skipped\": 0, \"task_total\": 2, \"needs_replan\": false}','2026-04-24 09:41:31'),(1423,'8cb77b84-628d-4b7c-9df7-8747d76bda78','phase','perception',66623,'{\"node\": \"perception\", \"event\": \"phase_enter\"}','2026-04-24 09:43:15'),(1424,'8cb77b84-628d-4b7c-9df7-8747d76bda78','phase','perception',66729,'{\"node\": \"perception\", \"event\": \"phase_exit\", \"slot_total\": 12, \"asking_slot\": null, \"slot_filled\": 9, \"intent_ready\": true, \"clarification_round\": 1}','2026-04-24 09:43:15'),(1425,'8cb77b84-628d-4b7c-9df7-8747d76bda78','decision','perception',66731,'{\"branch\": \"proceed\", \"reason\": \"意图就绪 → planning\"}','2026-04-24 09:43:15'),(1426,'8cb77b84-628d-4b7c-9df7-8747d76bda78','phase','planning',86321,'{\"node\": \"planning\", \"event\": \"phase_enter\"}','2026-04-24 09:43:35'),(1427,'8cb77b84-628d-4b7c-9df7-8747d76bda78','phase','planning',86437,'{\"node\": \"planning\", \"event\": \"phase_exit\", \"plan_ready\": true, \"task_count\": 3, \"plan